channel.title: Sprites not showing up ingame
channel.description: My friend and I are currently working on a server together and we are having trouble with a number of sprites not showing up ingame. We are using trisidiax as our server base. Things such as emote icons, the X in the top right of the bank and the buttons at the bottom of the equipment tab are not appearing. Any help with being able to locate and load these sprites would be appreciated.
